D3 Security System App for D3 Dashboard

-------------------------------------------------------
## Introduction:

This App displays event summary on D3 dashboard for the D3 related events

-------------------------------------------------------
## Installation and Setup

- In Splunk, navigate to the app manager page. Click "Install app from file" and upload the D3 App.
- Navigate to app manager page, click "Set up" on "D3 Cyber Incident Reponse Dashboard" row. Fill out all configuration settings and click "Save". 

